    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211000/extras/604e29359502e4dbd67bc50b0f696d61.avif?t=1771244694\" width=640 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>中文（简体）:</strong><br>雅各布·米勒的生活一团糟，没有未来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一切将在他收到参加一款新食品产品最后阶段试验的邀请后改变。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在为期十天的试验期间，参与者将经历一套奇特的身体与感官刺激计划，这套计划基于对食品生产与人类营养的新理解。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >试验将在 Spira 食品与营养设施中全程隔离进行。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成为改变人类未来的一部分，成为 Spira 的一员。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211000/extras/131b3b93c6d8d749a19a6148905f055a.poster.avif?t=1771244694\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211000/extras/131b3b93c6d8d749a19a6148905f055a.webm?t=1771244694\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211000/extras/131b3b93c6d8d749a19a6148905f055a.mp4?t=1771244694\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>中文（简体）:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《INANIMA》是一款经典的像素风格生存恐怖游戏。解开谜题，探索秘密，并面对噩梦般的生物，在保全生命与理智的同时，奋力求生。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211000/extras/786b5ef6a0a4dd500fb21e96416fee91.poster.avif?t=1771244694\" width=400 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211000/extras/786b5ef6a0a4dd500fb21e96416fee91.webm?t=1771244694\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211000/extras/786b5ef6a0a4dd500fb21e96416fee91.mp4?t=1771244694\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>中文（简体）:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >细致的像素艺术美术风格，配合动态光影效果。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拥有多种远程与近战武器的战斗系统。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >瞄准敌人的关键部位造成更高伤害，或射击肢体以减缓其行动速度。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用资源升级武器与装备，让武器更强大或更精准。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可怕的敌人会根据环境调整行为模式。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >敌人对光线和声音敏感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211000/extras/ad000f0994911245c0531396ab71cce3.poster.avif?t=1771244694\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211000/extras/ad000f0994911245c0531396ab71cce3.webm?t=1771244694\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211000/extras/ad000f0994911245c0531396ab71cce3.mp4?t=1771244694\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211000/extras/0842f8b9c375b1c4a14e72d019eda891.avif?t=1771244694\" width=640 height=100 /></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
